title: What Happens in China (2011)
description:
Great for those interested in the kind of trips the Explorica educational travel agency has to offer!

---------------- This is real. This is China. ----------------

In April of 2011, a group of Chinese language students from Quabbin Regional High School in the small town of Barre, Massachusetts boarded a plane bound for Beijing, China. There they spent ten days immersed in a foreign culture. They toured the cities of Beijing, Xi'an, Guilin, and Shanghai, making new friends along the way. Yet many had never even traveled before... what will happen when Quabbin meets China?

Director Tyler Nickerson takes us through his own experiences from the trip using text and voice narration throughout the film. Five months in the making, 'What Happens in China' is sure to warm your heart.
